助教資訊 Contact with Tutor


學習規範 Course Policy
	    In this industry-academy cooperation program students can incorporate their academic background with the practical training of various trades in EMO. They can familiarize themselves with aircraft maintenance as well as planning control procedures and later put what they have learned into practice in their future professions.      

