有關課程其他調查 Other Surveys of Courses
                   1.本課程是否規劃業界教師參與教學或演講?   是，約 12 次            
Is there any industry specialist invited in this course? How many times? Yes, about 12 times.
			
           2.本課程是否規劃內含校外實習 (並非參訪)?   是，約 30 天		   
Is there any in (out of) school practicum involved in this course? How many hours?  Yes, about 30 days.












 
